## This file is the .pot template for the phoenix_kit_newsletters
## "default" Gettext domain. msgids here are tab/group labels and
## admin-panel UI strings registered with
## `gettext_backend: PhoenixKit.Newsletters.Gettext`.
##
## Tab labels are not extracted automatically by `mix gettext.extract`
## (they live as plain strings in `Tab.new!(label: ...)`, not in a
## `dgettext` macro call), so this template is maintained manually.
## When you add a new translatable label, add the msgid here and run
## `mix gettext.merge priv/gettext` to propagate to every locale's
## `default.po`.

